Package: SeuratExplorer
Title: An Interactive Shiny App for Visualizing scRNAseq Data Processed in Seurat
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Reed", "Crocker", "Reed.Crocker@childrens.harvard.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Reed Crocker <Reed.Crocker@childrens.harvard.edu>
Description: A simple, one-command package which runs an interactive shiny dashboard capable of common visualizations for single cell RNAseq. The application requires a pre-processed Seurat object, saved as an RDS file.
License: use_mit_license()
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.1.2
Imports:
    dplyr,
    ggplot2,
    purrr,
    Seurat,
    shiny,
    shinydashboard,
    stringr
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)